{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/how-to-use/error/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"보통사람","author":"pej4303"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f8e1239c-1f2d-55df-a619-99c5acdcde6d","excerpt":"1. 현상 개발서버 https 적용으로 아래와 같이 http 요청 블락 에러가 발생하였다. 그래서 아래의 메타 태그를 추가해 줬다.  하지만 개발서버 https 적용을 해제하면서부터 화면 접속시 자동으로  로 붙어서 js, css를 읽는 경우가 발생하였다. 2. 원인 https…","html":"<h2 id=\"1-현상\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81\" aria-label=\"1 현상 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 현상</h2>\n<p>개발서버 https 적용으로 아래와 같이 http 요청 블락 에러가 발생하였다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">This request has been blocked; the content must be served over HTTPS.</code></pre></div>\n<p>그래서 아래의 메타 태그를 추가해 줬다. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">http-equiv</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Content-Security-Policy<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>upgrade-insecure-requests<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>하지만 개발서버 https 적용을 해제하면서부터 화면 접속시 자동으로 <code class=\"language-text\">https://</code> 로 붙어서 js, css를 읽는 경우가 발생하였다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-원인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%9B%90%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"2 원인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 원인</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">http-equiv</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Content-Security-Policy<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>upgrade-insecure-requests<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>https때문에 추가했던 메타 태그의 문제로, content-security-policy를 설정할 경우 자동으로 https로 호출해 주는 것이었다. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">The HTTP Content-Security-Policy (CSP) upgrade-insecure-requests directive instructs user agents to treat all of a site's insecure URLs (those served over HTTP) as though they have been replaced with secure URLs (those served over HTTPS).\r\nHTTP Content-Security-Policy(CSP) upgrade-insecure-requests</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"3 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 해결</h2>\n<p>해당 태그를 주석처리 하면 현상은 해결되지만, 개발서버에 https 적용 시 http 요청 블락 에러를 이 방법 말고 다른 방법으로 해야 될 것 같다. 로컬은 http인데 개발서버는 https인 경우에는 이 메타태그를 사용하는 것은 좋은 방법이 아닌 것 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>참조\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/upgrade-insecure-requests\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/upgrade-insecure-requests</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81\">1. 현상</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%EC%9B%90%EC%9D%B8\">2. 원인</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\">3. 해결</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[오류] 자동으로 도메인에 https가 붙는 경우","description":"자동으로 도메인에 https가 붙는 경우","date":"August 23, 2024","tags":["Error","Web"],"series":"오류 모음집","previewImage":null,"isPrivate":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/how-to-use/writing-posts/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to Write Markdown Posts? ✍️","isPrivate":null}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"f8e1239c-1f2d-55df-a619-99c5acdcde6d","previousPostId":"ae43e3ea-dd3e-5c78-95d1-ebfa284215a0","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slice